<rdf:Description
    rdf:about="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/805"
    trackback:ping="http://www.notapathetic.com/cgi-bin/trackback.cgi/805"
    dc:title="I live in a "safe seat"."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/805"
    dc:description="I live in a "safe seat".  What's the point of voting when there is  simply no possibility whatsoever that my vote could change anything?

